_sText:
Hey peoples,

This is a hostage rescue map where the counter-terrorists raid the terrorists headquarters to rescue the hostages. The terrorist HQ is a three story building with a garage, tech room (with 16 beefy computers) and a storage room at the top. The terrorists must defend there HQ at all costs.

This map took me a while to make and i made sure it was my best one yet. Please leave comments.

Enjoy :)
